1
00:01:20,860 --> 00:01:26,800
[Love Endures]

2
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:29,300
[Episode 6]

3
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:39,840
Zhou, what's going on?

4
00:01:40,390 --> 00:01:40,950
Yingzi,

5
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:43,920
Look at this week's work schedule.

6
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:46,230
Wasn't the "Bridesmaids for Rent" project
yours?

7
00:01:46,230 --> 00:01:47,640
Why are they using Song Ke's script?

8
00:01:58,750 --> 00:01:59,310
Morning.

9
00:01:59,590 --> 00:02:00,480
Morning, Yingzhi.

10
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:06,560
Morning.

11
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:11,800
Yingzi, your coffee.

12
00:02:13,670 --> 00:02:15,040
Please don't get mad.

13
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:17,480
I really meant to help you
gather information.

14
00:02:17,480 --> 00:02:19,640
I didn't mean to send my script
to the editor.

15
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:22,480
I'm not mad.

16
00:02:23,230 --> 00:02:23,950
Yiran,

17
00:02:24,509 --> 00:02:25,480
tell me.

18
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:27,230
How's it going with Ding Ye?

19
00:02:27,670 --> 00:02:28,950
I've tried to interview Ding Ye

20
00:02:28,950 --> 00:02:30,080
and contact him many times.

21
00:02:30,390 --> 00:02:32,080
He didn't even reply to my messages.

22
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,200
Let's not say about meeting him.

23
00:02:33,390 --> 00:02:34,670
Let's discuss about this.

24
00:02:35,230 --> 00:02:36,320
This topic,

25
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:38,230
is it worth our time

26
00:02:38,230 --> 00:02:39,230
and energy?

27
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:42,430
I have a different opinion
than Yiran's this time.

28
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:45,320
Ding Ye

29
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:46,600
has a strange mind.

30
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:47,640
He contacted

31
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:49,200
the media which exposed him

32
00:02:49,200 --> 00:02:50,040
for molesting
a drunken female passenger.

33
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:52,080
But he didn't ask the media
to clarify anything.

34
00:02:52,390 --> 00:02:53,390
Instead, he requested the media

35
00:02:53,390 --> 00:02:55,920
to remove the picture
of the female passenger.

36
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:57,800
He didn't care about his own innocence.

37
00:02:57,800 --> 00:03:00,040
Instead, he's worried
about the girl's reputation.

38
00:03:00,830 --> 00:03:04,390
I'm getting more curious about this guy.

39
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:06,830
This matter

40
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:08,920
got you a chance to publish.

41
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:10,950
I got a windfall too.

42
00:03:12,390 --> 00:03:13,320
At least

43
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,640
I got to know you better.

44
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:50,760
Yiran.

45
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,270
Is everything going well with Ding Ye?

46
00:04:00,990 --> 00:04:02,160
Are you concerned about me

47
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,230
or Ding Ye?

48
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:06,600
If you are able to help Ding Ye

49
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,760
clear his name,

50
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,830
helping you to complete the interview
as quickly as possible

51
00:04:10,830 --> 00:04:11,830
is what I would like to do.

52
00:04:12,270 --> 00:04:14,360
Couldn't you realise
after what Song Ke did?

53
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,670
There is only competition
at the workplace.

54
00:04:15,670 --> 00:04:16,720
Nobody is your friend.

55
00:04:17,230 --> 00:04:18,630
Since you're concerned
about Ding Ye so much,

56
00:04:18,990 --> 00:04:20,630
why not try again?

57
00:04:22,230 --> 00:04:23,750
I got rejected before.

58
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:29,230
You only got rejected once
for your favourite topic

59
00:04:29,230 --> 00:04:30,160
and now you're giving up?

60
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,960
You didn't even fight back
when people did you wrong.

61
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,480
Do you think that sitting here

62
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,550
would help you forget everything?

63
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,280
I actually have my own way.

64
00:04:44,870 --> 00:04:46,800
Whenever I feel wronged and sad,

65
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:48,990
I'd think of myself as Thanos.

66
00:04:48,990 --> 00:04:50,110
With a snap of my fingers,

67
00:04:50,110 --> 00:04:51,990
I could wipe out half of the people
on Earth.

68
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:54,110
Thinking it this way,

69
00:04:54,670 --> 00:04:56,750
Song Ke is nothing.

70
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:02,310
You're not Thanos.

71
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:04,360
You're clearly a coward.

72
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:06,870
You can only comfort yourself

73
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:08,070
without changing nothing.

74
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:08,800
Well,

75
00:05:09,870 --> 00:05:11,800
did He Ping's matter defeat you?

76
00:05:19,670 --> 00:05:21,360
I'll give you Ding Ye's topic,

77
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,550
how about that?

78
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:28,310
Aren't you working on Ding Ye's topic?

79
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:30,920
It's normal to swap unfit topics

80
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,630
among colleagues.

81
00:05:33,070 --> 00:05:34,920
The best counterattack at the workplace

82
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,840
is to showcase your expertise.

83
00:05:37,750 --> 00:05:38,720
If you're okay with that,

84
00:05:39,069 --> 00:05:40,429
I'll convince the chief editors.

85
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,840
Thank you, Yiran.

86
00:05:48,550 --> 00:05:49,480
I'll try my best.

87
00:05:50,190 --> 00:05:50,630
I'm heading back to work.

88
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,520
The house has been empty for some time.

89
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,720
It's a bit far from the subway.

90
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,070
That's why it's hard to rent it out.

91
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,280
It doesn't matter.

92
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,160
If you want to rent it,

93
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,670
the owner can furnish it
with new furniture.

94
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:20,550
That's fine.

95
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,360
This area

96
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,720
is newly developed in recent years.

97
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,480
Greening is great here.

98
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,600
The view is great, too.

99
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:27,520
Sir?

100
00:06:28,070 --> 00:06:28,840
Sir?

101
00:06:30,870 --> 00:06:31,990
If you're not satisfied with this one,

102
00:06:31,990 --> 00:06:33,280
there are two other apartments
in this area

103
00:06:33,280 --> 00:06:34,110
to choose from.

104
00:06:35,110 --> 00:06:36,160
It's okay.

105
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,040
This one will do.

106
00:06:40,630 --> 00:06:41,400
Excuse me,

107
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:42,400
let me answer a call.

108
00:06:47,670 --> 00:06:49,280
Why didn't you tell me
you're in Jiangzhou?

109
00:06:51,190 --> 00:06:52,230
Did Zhuang Yuan tell you?

110
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:53,800
He even told me

111
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:56,040
you are looking for a job
at a local gaming company.

112
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:58,160
I haven't made a decision yet.

113
00:06:59,230 --> 00:07:01,190
Tell me if you have a preferred company.

114
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,840
I work in the media industry,
I have big connection.

115
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:05,310
I might be able to help you.

116
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:07,160
Moreover,

117
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:08,870
given your capabilities,

118
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:10,360
if I introduce you to a company,

119
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,040
they will surely thank me for that.

120
00:07:12,430 --> 00:07:12,960
Sure.

121
00:07:13,520 --> 00:07:14,160
Thank you.

122
00:07:15,550 --> 00:07:16,870
Let's have a meal together soon.

123
00:07:17,190 --> 00:07:17,870
Sure.

124
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:18,920
Well, I'll get back to work now.

125
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:19,840
Bye.

126
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:35,800
(A genius writer)

127
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:38,720
who disappeared for more than ten years,

128
00:07:39,870 --> 00:07:40,960
where did he go?

129
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,720
Hunter, don't simply shoot.

130
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:02,750
Follow my commands.

131
00:08:06,230 --> 00:08:07,360
What's wrong with you guys?

132
00:08:07,630 --> 00:08:09,230
You played poorly
and didn't follow my commands.

133
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:12,430
You won't get paid for this match.

134
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,230
Yi,

135
00:08:14,230 --> 00:08:15,280
don't be angry.

136
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:16,840
They are all newbies.

137
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:18,840
I'm not angry,

138
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:20,110
I'm just about to vomit blood.

139
00:08:20,110 --> 00:08:22,550
Yi is the best player
in Hangtian City Warcraft.

140
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,990
He's going to compete in Jiangzhou
this weekend.

141
00:08:24,990 --> 00:08:26,800
He might be the national champion.

142
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:28,430
All right, stop it.

143
00:08:28,670 --> 00:08:29,960
That's just an invitational tournament.

144
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,470
Yi, don't be modest.

145
00:08:32,470 --> 00:08:34,470
You're pretty awesome.

146
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:38,040
How long have we been playing?

147
00:08:38,920 --> 00:08:39,590
Fatty,

148
00:08:40,670 --> 00:08:41,710
get me two bowls of fried noodles.

149
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,070
What are you doing here?

150
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:48,880
You've been playing video games
for four hours.

151
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:50,120
I thought you might be hungry.

152
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,000
Tell me.

153
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,310
How do you intend to kill me?

154
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,800
Are you going to compete in Jiangzhou?

155
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,190
Can you take me with you?

156
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,880
I said, no!

157
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:05,120
I'll be your assistant.

158
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,400
I'll serve tea, do the laundry,
and cook.

159
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,520
I'm going for a tournament.

160
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:08,520
Why do you want to come along?

161
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,350
I want to go to Jiangzhou.

162
00:09:09,350 --> 00:09:10,310
There is an aquarium in Jiangzhou.

163
00:09:10,310 --> 00:09:11,520
I want to see whales.

164
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:12,920
What does that have to do with me?

165
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:13,830
I like whales.

166
00:09:13,830 --> 00:09:14,920
You do know about this.

167
00:09:14,920 --> 00:09:15,430
By the way,

168
00:09:15,430 --> 00:09:17,310
there are no whales at the aquarium!

169
00:09:17,310 --> 00:09:18,240
There are!

170
00:09:19,190 --> 00:09:19,950
Don't forget

171
00:09:19,950 --> 00:09:21,430
I used to help you with your homework.

172
00:09:21,430 --> 00:09:22,350
Please.

173
00:09:23,310 --> 00:09:23,830
How about this?

174
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:26,190
Before you graduate,

175
00:09:26,190 --> 00:09:27,400
I'll help you with all your homework.

176
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:30,590
Please.

177
00:09:30,590 --> 00:09:30,880
It's just that

178
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:31,550
the organizer

179
00:09:31,550 --> 00:09:33,040
only gave me a room.

180
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,190
Where are you going to stay, then?

181
00:09:34,190 --> 00:09:35,640
I can get another room.

182
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:36,310
I will cover the expenses myself.

183
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:38,120
Do you have an ID?

184
00:09:40,430 --> 00:09:41,590
I can sleep on the couch.

185
00:09:41,590 --> 00:09:43,120
I can even sleep on a desk.

186
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:47,800
Please.

187
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:49,040
All the homework given
before graduation,

188
00:09:49,040 --> 00:09:50,070
you'll help me with it, right?

189
00:09:50,070 --> 00:09:51,040
I promise!

190
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:52,540
How about serving tea,
doing the laundry, and cooking?

191
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,550
You promise?

192
00:09:53,550 --> 00:09:54,350
I promise.

193
00:09:58,760 --> 00:09:59,350
Fine, then.

194
00:10:00,070 --> 00:10:00,950
Have you agreed?

195
00:10:01,469 --> 00:10:02,519
Is that a yes?

196
00:10:58,190 --> 00:10:59,190
How generous of you

197
00:10:59,190 --> 00:11:00,550
to have bought me ice cream.

198
00:11:03,590 --> 00:11:05,120
If you win the tournament,

199
00:11:05,670 --> 00:11:06,710
do you get prize money?

200
00:11:07,040 --> 00:11:07,830
Sure.

201
00:11:07,830 --> 00:11:08,670
A thousand yuan.

202
00:11:09,470 --> 00:11:10,400
A thousand?

203
00:11:12,070 --> 00:11:13,800
More than my New Year's money.

204
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:16,880
If I were to give you a thousand yuan,

205
00:11:16,880 --> 00:11:18,120
how are you going to spend it?

206
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:22,040
If I have a thousand yuan,

207
00:11:22,590 --> 00:11:25,310
I'll buy a new pair of dancing shoes
for Yifei.

208
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:26,590
Mingyu

209
00:11:26,590 --> 00:11:27,470
always skip meals,

210
00:11:27,470 --> 00:11:29,190
so I'll buy her a thermos.

211
00:11:29,710 --> 00:11:31,120
Guan Chao loves Kobe,

212
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:32,800
so I'll buy him a Lakers jersey.

213
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,160
How about Zhuang Yuan?

214
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:39,920
Zhuang Yuan

215
00:11:39,920 --> 00:11:41,070
loves learning so much,

216
00:11:41,400 --> 00:11:42,430
I'll buy him

217
00:11:42,670 --> 00:11:44,160
a set of mock examination workbooks.

218
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:50,920
Do you like smart guys?

219
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,760
Smart guys are not bad.

220
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:55,710
But

221
00:11:56,310 --> 00:11:57,280
they're not my type.

222
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,000
Why?

223
00:12:00,830 --> 00:12:03,120
I am used to being free and easygoing.

224
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,000
I don't understand

225
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:04,950
smart people.

226
00:12:05,470 --> 00:12:07,520
A like-minded person

227
00:12:07,520 --> 00:12:08,430
who can enjoy meals with me

228
00:12:08,430 --> 00:12:09,350
and have fun with me till I'm old

229
00:12:09,590 --> 00:12:10,520
suits me well.

230
00:12:14,590 --> 00:12:15,640
What are you laughing at?

231
00:12:16,070 --> 00:12:17,800
You're a grown man,
why are you being so nosy?

232
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:20,550
You haven't told me yet.

233
00:12:20,950 --> 00:12:22,520
What are you going to buy for yourself?

234
00:12:25,190 --> 00:12:26,640
I'll buy a MP3 player

235
00:12:27,350 --> 00:12:29,310
for myself.

236
00:12:29,310 --> 00:12:30,310
So I can listen to Stefanie Sun's songs

237
00:12:30,310 --> 00:12:31,430
whenever I want.

238
00:12:32,590 --> 00:12:33,670
Nothing else?

239
00:12:36,310 --> 00:12:37,040
Wait a minute.

240
00:12:47,070 --> 00:12:47,950
And this.

241
00:12:49,670 --> 00:12:50,470
I know him.

242
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,800
He is your favourite writer.

243
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:53,590
March 9th?

244
00:12:53,590 --> 00:12:54,950
March 9th is...

245
00:12:59,470 --> 00:13:00,430
After all this,

246
00:13:00,430 --> 00:13:02,000
you came to Jiangzhou just for this?

247
00:13:15,710 --> 00:13:16,550
I'll sleep on the couch.

248
00:13:18,760 --> 00:13:19,760
Are you sure?

249
00:13:20,190 --> 00:13:21,350
Yes.

250
00:13:21,350 --> 00:13:22,430
I am short.

251
00:13:22,430 --> 00:13:24,280
Let me put a pillow here.

252
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:25,470
Here you go, a tiny bed.

253
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:26,760
It's comfortable.

254
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:29,670
Don't fight with me over it.

255
00:13:29,670 --> 00:13:30,550
When I was at home,

256
00:13:30,550 --> 00:13:32,040
I'd sleep on the couch
when I was watching TV.

257
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:33,040
It's comfortable.

258
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:35,670
I know.

259
00:13:36,190 --> 00:13:37,470
I wasn't trying to fight with you
over it.

260
00:13:38,710 --> 00:13:40,190
What I'm trying to say is,

261
00:13:40,190 --> 00:13:41,280
when I sleep,

262
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:42,920
I usually sleep on two pillows.

263
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,120
So...

264
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:51,640
Don't disturb my sleep.

265
00:13:51,640 --> 00:13:52,670
I have a tournament tomorrow.

266
00:13:54,640 --> 00:13:55,280
Got it.

267
00:13:57,470 --> 00:13:58,470
I sleep with my bag.

268
00:14:19,640 --> 00:14:21,400
Isn't Stefanie Sun your idol?

269
00:14:23,040 --> 00:14:24,400
She is my musical idol.

270
00:14:25,070 --> 00:14:27,310
Ding Ye is my literary idol.

271
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:30,120
Don't tell me you came all the way here

272
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:32,120
just to get his autograph.

273
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:32,950
Ten years later,

274
00:14:32,950 --> 00:14:34,950
he will definitely be a great writer.

275
00:14:34,950 --> 00:14:36,830
His signature will be very valuable.

276
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:41,430
Actually...

277
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:43,520
After reading his book,

278
00:14:43,800 --> 00:14:45,400
I have a lot of questions for him.

279
00:14:47,430 --> 00:14:48,350
Did he write so badly?

280
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,550
It's so well written!

281
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:52,160
He inspired me to explore things.

282
00:14:55,070 --> 00:14:56,880
Well, have fun exploring things.

283
00:14:59,590 --> 00:15:01,470
I think reading his book

284
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,830
would make me like him for who he is.

285
00:15:05,640 --> 00:15:06,920
You should go after him.

