312
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,670
while crustaceans

313
00:16:04,670 --> 00:16:06,520
take shelter in its skeleton.

314
00:16:06,880 --> 00:16:08,240
A whale's bones

315
00:16:08,760 --> 00:16:11,520
