a source of energy for bacteria.

316
00:16:13,710 --> 00:16:15,070
This is what we call a whale fall.

317
00:16:18,040 --> 00:16:19,880
Whales are the most gentle miracle

318
00:16:20,640 --> 00:16:22,190
in the sea.

319
00:16:23,520 --> 00:16:24,120
No,

320
00:16:25,190 --> 00:16:27,640
